T*
() Tj
T*
(Atho?s monetary system is explicit and integer-based. The network uses atomic units \(atoms\) for) Tj
T*
(consensus-critical accounting and does not rely on floating-point arithmetic in value rules.) Tj
T*
(This avoids rounding drift and makes audits easier.) Tj
T*
() Tj
