T*
(- pre-tail base target: 400,000,000 ATHO,) Tj
T*
(- hard max emitted supply: 500,000,000 ATHO,) Tj
T*
(- supply floor guardrail: 21,000,000 ATHO,) Tj
T*
(- bootstrap allocation: 781,250 ATHO at block 1,) Tj
T*
(- tail start at height 17,000,000.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Before tail start, block rewards follow a stepped era schedule. At tail start, reward behavior) Tj
T*
(transitions to a lower fixed reward path \(0.1953125 ATHO/block\) and fee-routing rules become) Tj
